{"word":"H3863 - לוּא - lûwʼ - loo - If - ஆனால்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>לוּא"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>lûwʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>loo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>If / ஆனால்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அந்த, ஆல், என்று, ஒருவேளை, உம், ஆ - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"if, Oh that.! If only.!"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Conjunction / இணைப்புச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A conditional particle; <i>if</i>; by implication (interjectionally as a wish) <i>would that!</i>: - if (haply), peradventure, I pray thee, though, I would, would God (that)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3863 - לוּא - lûwʼ - loo/3863\">H3863</a>, <a href=\"#/H3864 - לוּבִי - Lûwbîy - loo-bee'/3864\">H3864</a>, <a href=\"#/H3865 - לוּד - Lûwd - lood/3865\">H3865</a>, <a href=\"#/H3866 - לוּדִי - Lûwdîy - loo-dee'/3866\">H3866</a>, <a href=\"#/H3884 - לוּלֵא - lûwlêʼ - loo-lay'/3884\">H3884</a>"}]}